        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code>   # 📢 功能更新清单 ！</code></pre><h3 id="1-音乐播放器功能"><a href="#1-音乐播放器功能" class="headerlink" title="1. 音乐播放器功能"></a>1. 音乐播放器功能</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```yaml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"># _config.butterfly.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">aplayer:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  enable: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  meting: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  asset_inject: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  per_page: false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  cdn:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    css: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer@1.10.1/dist/APlayer.min.css</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    js: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer@1.10.1/dist/APlayer.min.js</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  meting_cdn: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/meting@2.0.1/dist/Meting.min.js</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">meting_js:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  enable: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  id: &quot;13587772451&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  server: &quot;netease&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  type: &quot;playlist&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  fixed: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  autoplay: false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  loop: &quot;all&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  volume: 0.7</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  storageName: &quot;meting_storage&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  audioProxy: &quot;https://api.injahow.cn/meting/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">  mobile:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    enable: true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    cover: true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>效果预览</strong>：</p><ul><li>左下角固定播放器</li><li>支持歌单列表展开</li><li>移动端自适应</li><li>音量记忆功能</li></ul><hr><h3 id="2-看板娘功能"><a href="#2-看板娘功能" class="headerlink" title="2. 看板娘功能"></a>2. 看板娘功能</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">yaml复制代码#</span> <span class="string">主题配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">live2d:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">pluginModelPath:</span> <span class="string">/live2dw/assets/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">model:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">use:</span> <span class="string">koharu</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">display:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">position:</span> <span class="string">left</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">width:</span> <span class="number">200</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">height:</span> <span class="number">350</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">mobile:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">show:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">dialog:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">script:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">欢迎来到我的博客！</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">需要帮助吗？</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>模型资源</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">复制代码/live2dw/</span><br><span class="line">├── assets/</span><br><span class="line">│   └── koharu.model.json</span><br><span class="line">└── lib/</span><br><span class="line">    └── L2Dwidget.min.js</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>特性</strong>：</p><ul><li>左侧悬浮二次元人物</li><li>智能对话功能</li><li>移动端可见</li><li>点击交互反馈</li></ul><hr><h3 id="3-评论系统"><a href="#3-评论系统" class="headerlink" title="3. 评论系统"></a>3. 评论系统</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">y复制代码#</span> <span class="string">_config.butterfly.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">waline:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">serverURL:</span> <span class="string">https://your-domain.com</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">lang:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">emoji:</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">https://unpkg.com/@waline/emojis/weibo</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">requiredMeta:</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">nick</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">mail</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">pageSize:</span> <span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">pageview:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>安全配置</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nginx复制代码<span class="comment"># Nginx 反向代理配置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">location</span> /comment &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">proxy_pass</span> https://waline.vercel.app;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">proxy_set_header</span> Host <span class="variable">$host</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">proxy_set_header</span> X-Real-IP <span class="variable">$remote_addr</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">proxy_set_header</span> X-Forwarded-For <span class="variable">$proxy_add_x_forwarded_for</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="🛠-部署注意事项"><a href="#🛠-部署注意事项" class="headerlink" title="🛠 部署注意事项"></a>🛠 部署注意事项</h2><ol><li><p><strong>依赖版本</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">json复制代码<span class="attr">&quot;dependencies&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;hexo&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^7.3.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-theme-butterfly&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^5.3.5&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-tag-aplayer&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^3.0.4&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-abbrlink&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^2.2.1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>缓存清理</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">复制代码hexo clean &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf public db.json .cache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>资源加载验证</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">javascript复制代码<span class="comment">// 控制台验证命令</span></span><br><span class="line">!!<span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;.aplayer&#x27;</span>) &amp;&amp; </span><br><span class="line">!!<span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;#waline&#x27;</span>) &amp;&amp; </span><br><span class="line">!!<span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;.live2d-widget&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo server</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
